{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "决战前夕，慕容在高台上俯瞰被驱离家园的流民，心生怜悯却转为愤怒。柳明秋识破铁大爷留灯虚张声势之计，决定只带一人突袭二十七处埋伏。他选中了慕容身边的蒙面侍女小苏——她决定以赤裸之身作为突袭武器，利用美色分散埋伏者注意力。小苏的表姐袖袖留在慕容身边为他按摩安抚。然而柳明秋突然倒下，割头小鬼再次出现割走了他的头颅。小苏惊晕，而慕容浑然不知，仍在高台上信心满满地等待捷报。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你说那两个乌龟一定已经走了，现在为什么还没有走?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "你看见了他们还在那里?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "你只不过看见那里还有灯而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "人不是灯。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "人走了，还是可以把灯点在那里的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "他们为什么要把灯点在那里?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为他们要让你认为他们一直都在那里等着你去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "他们在，你当然就不会去，在决战日之前，那二十九个人就可以平平安安的埋伏在那里了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "你看见那里的灯火，你的心不定，他们才能好好的回去休养，以逸待劳，以静制动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "如果你去了，万一发现他们的一处埋伏，他们还有什么好玩的?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "对他们来说，那实在很好玩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "他们觉得不好玩的时候，应该就是我们觉得最好玩的时候，对不对?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "那么我们是不是应该立刻就去?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "好，我听你的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你现在就去，带二十九个高手去，把他们那二十七处埋伏，全都连根拔出来。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "那倒不必。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "不必?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "为什么不必?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我根本不必带二十九个人去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为那二十七处埋伏处，相隔有一段距离，而且全都极为隐秘。没有听到他们事先约定的讯号时，谁也不敢轻举妄动，贸然现身。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "所以我们去攻他第一处埋伏时，另外的埋伏处根本不会知道。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我发觉他们的埋伏时，一招内就一定要致他们的死命，那只是一瞬间的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我可以保证，这二十七处埋伏中的二十九个人，在临死前连一点声音都不会发出来。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "如果我带二十九个人，反而会惊动他们，那就是打草惊蛇，反而弄巧成拙了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "有理!",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "所以我只要带一个人去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "只带一个人?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "二十七处埋伏，二十九个人，其中至少有两个埋伏中有两个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "以一敌二，虽然不难，以二制二，才万无一失。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我是不是应该带一位高手去?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你当然要带一个高手去，而且一定要是一个高手中的高手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "公子手下，高手如云，可是我要带走的这一位，却不知公子是不是肯放人?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你要带的是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我要带去的就是她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你这个不瞎的瞎子，真有一套，你不但有思想有头脑，而且有眼力。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我佩服你，可是我一点都不喜欢你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "这个世界上，喜欢我的人本来就不多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为大家都觉得我太聪明了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我结识的都是聪明人，如果他认为我比他还聪明，他怎么会喜欢我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "幸好这一点并不重要，别人喜不喜欢你，都没有什么关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为我有用。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "一个真正有用的人，别人是不是喜欢他，他全都可以不在乎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我的想法也是这样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我姓苏，别人都叫我小苏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你知道?你怎么会知道?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "我知道的事也许远比你想像中要多得多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "现在你是不是已经可以让我看一看了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "看什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "看你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "现在我能看到的，只不过是一块蒙面的青布巾，和一件直统统的袍子而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你还想看什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "看你的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "我知道你和你的表姐都是不能让慕容看见的，因为他已经不能再受到一点刺激，对他来说，一个年轻漂亮的女孩子已经是种要命的刺激了，何况两个。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "我不是慕容，我可以受得了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "所以现在你一定要让我看看你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "你知不知道你有一样大多数女人都没有的东西?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "而且我还知道我有的不止一样。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我有好身材，我有好皮肤，我还有一种可以让男人心跳的魅力!",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "你知不知道你所有的这些，都是武器?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "尤其是对付男人，这些武器远比世上任何兵刃都犀利得多。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "一个女人如果要用刀剑来对付男人，这个女人非但一定丑得要命，而且一定蠢得要命。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "就好像一个总认为只要用钱就可以征服所有女人的男人一样蠢。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "你好像很了解自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我一直都很了解自己，而且尽力要让自己了解自己。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "因为一个女人如果不了解自己，就要上男人的当了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "那么，你是不是也知道你应。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "该用什么方法来善用你的这些武器?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我跟你去突袭时，我就这样子去，赤裸裸的去。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "难怪慕容说，我是个有眼光的人，我果然没有看错你。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "你的确没有让我失望。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_xiu_xiu",
      "text": "我错了。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_xiu_xiu",
      "text": "这一次我一定做错了。我该死，袖袖，现在我只恨不得你能杀了我。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiu_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "袖袖",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "你没有错，也没有看错人，你做的每一件事，都是对的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiu_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "袖袖",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我可以保证，这一次你的计划，一定可以成功。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我们为什么不能再等一下?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "等到天快亮的时候再出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "我们为什么要等?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "因为有经验的人都应该知道，天快亮的时候总是最黑暗的时候，也是在紧张中守候的人们最疲倦的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "在这种时候去突袭，成功的机会是不是更大?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "天亮前也是男人们情感最亢奋的时候，我甚至可以想像得到，他们其中一定有很多人会在这段时间里自渎。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我是个很好看的女人，我常常会接触到一些正常而健康的男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我对他们大概要比你了解得多一点。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "你说的有理。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "非常有理。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "那么我们是不是应该等一下再去?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "我们不等。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_su",
      "speaker_name": "小苏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "因为我们如果再等下去，我恐怕就会去做一些不该做的事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_su",
      "text": "在行动之前，我们最好不要再消耗体力!",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我相信柳先生的行动现在一定已经开始了，而且一定成功。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    }
